From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 11:08:42 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Two-tier sidebar: dark icon rail + light filter panel

- Dark icon rail (logo + nav icons, selected highlighted) on the far left
- Light-gray secondary panel on problem screens with Status/Difficulty
  groups, per-item count badges, and gradient-accent selection pills
- Status/difficulty filtering moved into the sidebar via URL query params
  (toggleable, combinable); search/tag/sort remain in the content bar
- Removable active-filter chips in the problems header
- Filter panel hidden on dashboard (full-width)
- New icons: target, circle/circle-dot/circle-check, refresh

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01JJ2ALpPXcgcr9CfdzcsDU4
